  "text": "The parameters and details of our ITRCN model are given in Table 5 . The model is trained on Adam optimizer [CITATION_1] . It is worth noting that the time lag is set to 5, which indicates that the interactive traffic states of the previous five time intervals are used to predict the interactive traffic state one time interval ahead. During the training process, the learning rate was set to 0.001.",
